Titolo: Ozma Wars

Anno: 1979

Descrizione: Ozma Wars (オズマ・ウオーズ, Ozuma Uōzu) is a shoot 'em up arcade game developed and released by Shin Nihon Kikaku (SNK) in 1979. Like Galaxian, Ozma Wars is a fixed shooter with a vertical scrolling background; the background scrolls, but the player ship's movement is restricted to the bottom of the screen.